39
) No other male secondary characters.

Specimens have been observed sitting on the ground or under low shrubs near ditches. Calling males were about 10 to 30 cm from the water (
Fig. 2
). The two adult females were found at a distance of 1-2 m from the ditch, in the grassy band near the road. Some male specimens were sitting on ferns and leaves about 20 cm above ground.
